      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must be greater than or equal to required level.",
      "rationale": "Model setup reviewed independently by two analysts. Boundary conditions, material assignments, and contact definitions verified against documented modeling protocol. Peer review checklist completed and archived. Use error risk judged low."
