      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must be greater than or equal to required level.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic material model appropriate for sub-yield loading regime. Titanium alloy (Ti-6Al-4V) modeled with isotropic elasticity; UHMWPE vertebral body surrogate modeled with published compressive modulus. Contact interfaces use penalty-based frictional formulation consistent with physical construct behavior. Model form uncertainty quantified via sensitivity analysis."
