      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 loading condition (static compression-bending at 5 mm/min). Required level 2 calls for at least two distinct test conditions to bound the operating envelope; only one condition available. This factor does not meet the required level and represents a documented credibility gap. Impact assessed as acceptable given that the COU is explicitly scoped to this single loading regime."
