      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison performed using both percent difference (<10% threshold) and validation metric E/uval (<1.96 threshold per ASME V&V 40 Section 9). All three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) pass both criteria across all 11 specimens. Statistical equivalence confirmed at 95% confidence level."
