    "rationale": "12 of 13 V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved level 1 vs. required level 2) is accepted on the basis that the COU is explicitly scoped to the single ASTM F1717 static compression-bending condition tested, and the overall credibility evidence is sufficient for a medium-risk regulatory decision. The FEA framework is accepted as credible for the stated COU.",
